{"tid":1203920,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"金鐘戒嚴的實況","createTime":"2019-06-11T13:46:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T13:49:53.000Z","uid":184722,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f8544662905e44e85ed818ea0f53b950ff04a92b","tid":1203920,"uid":184722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:46:54.000Z","msg":"金鐘嘅戒嚴實況就係一班連讀書都讀唔掂、智力低下嘅垃圾畜牲，得到絕對武力同權力嘅結果。<br />\n<br />\n佢地從來都無委屈，從來都無猶豫，從來都心甘情願，領取同自己智力、能力同貢獻都不相稱嘅高額薪酬，去成為當權者嘅工具。<br />\n<br />\n好多年前都已經講過，無需去體諒前線嘅警犬，唔好天真，可惜一切都成為歷史。<br />\n<br />\n五年後嘅今日，香港軍政府成立，除左叫大家唔好死之外，都諗唔到可以講咩。<br />\n<br />\n轉載自<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10156123204121994&amp;id=700731993\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10156123204121994%26id%3D700731993&d=%2FodnS2mEGvHoUZPzyf%2FmNT4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=8a0be126\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10156123204121994&amp;id=700731993</a>"},{"pid":"56e7305bcc577fc12747660217ebdf3556454480","tid":1203920,"uid":258566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:49:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}